University of the Year (Times Higher Education Awards 2018)                                                                                                                     Top 15 for Electronic Engineering (TGUG 2019)                                                                                                                   Study abroad and industry placement year opportunities                                                                                                                   88% of our students are in professional employment or postgraduate study within six months of graduating from Essex (DLHE 2017)                                                                                                                   Specialist labs and facilities                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             Undergraduate study                                                   Unexpectedly creative                     Flexible, accredited courses allowing you to choose your own path of specialisation.
Masters study                                                   Driven by imagination                     Explore our specialist taught Masters courses, combining formal instruction with a supervised research project.
PhD study                                                   A creative powerhouse                     We provide an active and stimulating environment to carry out your doctoral research and have an extensive range of specialist labs and facilities.
The CSEE community, both students and staff, are committed to making wonderful things for the benefit of society.
Our education and research strengths are based on people working together in a safe environment, designed to provide inquisitive minds with the opportunities to use their imagination to be creative.
Come along for the ride of your life!
Professor Anthony Vickers                                 Head of school                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Expertise for business                   Use our research to help you innovate - from placements and internships to Knowledge Transfer Partnerships.
WISE membership                   We have joined the WISE campaign to help us progress our gender equality work.
Membership means we can raise the profile of our female STEM staff as WISE role models and link them to our community.
Career Development                   In response to the University Athena SWAN initiative, a selection of resources were created offering support networks, training and funding opportunities specifically for women.
